Competition: Olympic Games
Season: 1908
BlockSource: http://rsssf.com/tableso/ol1908f.html

Round: First Round

19/10/1908; Hungary; np; Netherlands
*NB: match not played, Hungary withdrew for financial reasons

19/10/1908; Denmark; 9-0; France B; Shepherds Bush, London; Thomas Kyle; 2000
(N.Middleboe 2, Wolfhagen 4, Bohr 2, S.Nielsen)
Denmark: Drescher - Buchwald, H.Hansen - Bohr, K.Middleboe(c), N.Middleboe - O.Nielsen, Lindgreen, S.Nielsen, Wolfhagen, Andersen.
France B: Desrousseaux - Verlet, Morillion - Destarac, Denis(cap), Bilot - Filez, Mathaux, Holgart, Jenicot, Eucher.

20/10/1908; Bohemia; np; France A
* NB: match not played, Bohemia's participation was prevented by Austria on the grounds that Bohemia had lost FIFA membership in spring 1908 (in other Olympic events, Bohemia entered; in total 23 Bohemian and only 7 Austrian athletes entered the Games).

20/10/1908; Great Britain; 12-1; Sweden; White City, London; John T. Ibottson; 2000
Hawkes 2, Chapman, Berry, Woodward 2, Stapley 2, Purnell 4); Bergström
Great Britain: Bailey - Corbett, Smith - Hunt, Chapman(cap), Hawkes - Berry, Woodward, Stapley, Purnell, Hardman.
Sweden: Bengtsson - Fjästad, Malm - Sven Olsson, Lindman(cap), Olof Ohlsson - Almkvist, Bergström, Gustafsson, Sven Ohlsson, Ansén.

Round: Semi-Finals

22/10/1908; Great Britain; 4-0; Netherlands; White City, London; John T. Howcroft; 6000
Stapley 37, Stapley 60, Stapley 64, Stapley 75;
Great Britain: Bailey - Corbett, Smith - Hunt, Chapman(cap), Hawkes - Berry, Woodward, Stapley, Purnell, Hardman.
Netherlands: Beeuwkes - Heijting, Otten - Sol, de Korver, Mundt (cap) - Welcker, Snethlage, Reeman, Thomée, de Bruyn Kops.

22/10/1908; Denmark; 17-1; France A; Shepherds Bush, London; Thomas P. Campbell; 1000
S.E. Nielsen 3' 4' 6' 39' 46' 48' 52' 64' 66' 76', Lindgreen 18' 37', N.Middleboe 68', Wolfhagen 60' 72' 82' 89'; Sartorius 16'
Denmark: Drescher - Buchwald, H.Hansen - Bohr, K.Middleboe(c), N.Middleboe - Gandil, Lindgreen, S.Nielsen, Wolfhagen, Rasmussen.
France: Tillette - Dubly, Wibaut - Georges Bayrou, L. Schubart, Renaux - Fenouillière, Cypres, François(cap), Albert, Sartorius.

Round: Bronze Medal
 
23/10/1908; Netherlands; 2-0; Sweden; Shepherds Bush, London; John H. Pearson; 1000
Reeman 6, Snethlage 58;
Netherlands: Beeuwkes - Heijting, Otten - Sol, de Korver(cap), Kok - Welcker, Snethlage, Reeman, Thomée, de Bruyn Kops.
Sweden: Bengtsson - Fjästad, Andersson - Sven Olsson, Lindman(cap), Lidén - Fagrell, Bergström, Sven Ohlsson, Gustafsson, Ansén.


Round: Final
24/10/1908; Great Britain; 2-0; Denmark; White City, London; John Lewis; 8000
Chapman 20, Woodward 46;
Great Britain: Bailey - Corbett, Smith - Hunt, Chapman(cap), Hawkes - Berry, Woodward, Stapley, Purnell, Hardman. 
Denmark: Drescher - Buchwald, H.Hansen - Bohr, K.Middleboe(c), N.Midlleboe - O.Nielsen, Lindgreen, S.Nielsen, Wolfhagen, Rasmussen.

